title: The Goo. Irish comedy series from Youtube
description:
Meet Jonesy and Dave. They are best mates and are in the middle of a 5 week bender. Jonesy has just broken up with his long term girlfriend while Dave has just been invited to his 10 year school reunion.

Join them as they answer the question 'What is The Goo?'

Great show that should have more of a following. If you like it please head on over to youtube and give them an ould follow, cheers.
